nt establishes, administers, owns, and operates eye care hospitals. Its Investment Activities segment engages in the investment activities. The company was formerly known as Almondz Capital & Management Services Limited. Avonmore Capital & Management Services Limited was incorporated in 1991 and is headquartered in New Delhi, India."}}